        {
            "title": "Coldplay演唱會｜港女專程澳洲回港睇騷  獲主音邀上台點歌兼抱抱：發緊夢咁!",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Coldplay演唱會｜港女專程澳洲回港睇騷 獲主音邀上台點歌兼抱抱：完全像發夢\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2dbbdddde24cb8b46869699fb3d2b4f3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040917403938022.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Coldplay演唱會｜港女專程澳洲回港睇騷 獲主音邀上台點歌兼抱抱：完全像發夢</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【英國樂隊Coldplay/香港演唱會/啟德體育園/Chris Martin】英國樂隊Coldplay昨日（8日）在啟德體育園主場館舉行首場演唱會，氣氛非常熱烈，有前排觀眾獲Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台，除獲得點歌機會及合唱外，更有幸得到Chris Martin擁抱一個。該名特意由澳洲回港的幸運觀眾今日（9日）在社文平台上發帖，驚嘆今次經歷「完全係發緊夢咁!」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3444815/Coldplay%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%8F%96%E7%A5%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92-%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E8%99%95%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B\">Coldplay香港演唱會懶人包︱一文看清場地規則、取票地點、交通安排 行李寄存處有兩個！</a>\n</p>\n<p>該名被Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台的幸運觀眾VICKY在社交平台「threads」發帖，指今次經歷「完全係發緊夢咁」，形容「打橫比人抬上台，打橫抬返入去」，並「成功獲得兩個抱抱 一首點歌」，甚至向Chris Martin示愛，稱「好好攬，滋潤咗我嘅小小心靈」、「超近距離望佢嘅藍眼睛，將我靈魂都吸走曬」，最後不禁感嘆「不枉我飛3749miles（約6033公里），黎(嚟)睇show」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"sthl-lr\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185817/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"VICKY被Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台合唱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbc3f4bd6f2a5b06b0022a615ed8656f/2025-04/980798709870.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        VICKY被Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台合唱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185816/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"VICKY被Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台合唱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c8c3a26aaa42b72c14af0135e0fefa2/2025-04/879798749870980890.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        VICKY被Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台合唱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185813/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"該名特意由澳洲回港的幸運觀眾VICKY今日（9日）在社交平台上發帖。threads擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6eb55121c336dc78618ba56fa849f0ac/2025-04/432408957453.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        該名特意由澳洲回港的幸運觀眾VICKY今日（9日）在社交平台上發帖。threads擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185804/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"VICKY獲Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台，獲得點歌機會及合唱。threads擷圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/50aac6ac3013512046e8f2e1fd815d9e/2025-04/84904844800489485610.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        VICKY獲Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台，獲得點歌機會及合唱。threads擷圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185806/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"VICKY獲Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台。threads圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e66653da0948f9110232e75c90409472/2025-04/68540684864065406854850.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        VICKY獲Coldplay主唱Chris Martin「點名」上台。threads圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185807/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"英國樂隊Coldplay昨日（8日）在啟德體育園主場館舉行首場演唱會。threads圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4e216f576eddf71c5d5041a43968441/2025-04/874987986418960496046501321.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英國樂隊Coldplay昨日（8日）在啟德體育園主場館舉行首場演唱會。threads圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185808/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"主唱Chris Martin觀看並分享VICKY三幅自行製造的橫額。threads圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c852a5bc278834b02a82a0fb562f6be4/2025-04/79897404849894089048904800135.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        主唱Chris Martin觀看並分享VICKY三幅自行製造的橫額。threads圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185809/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"主唱Chris Martin觀看並分享VICKY三幅自行製造的橫額。threads圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea449ab9c804068db9472f0d517c3481/2025-04/887967496464160.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        主唱Chris Martin觀看並分享VICKY三幅自行製造的橫額。threads圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185810/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/519e39f67cbe05619f3e9361fd21a3e2/2025-04/85864864864846.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>VICKY的好友亦在該帖下留言，點明她今次特意由澳洲回港，指她「不枉山長水遠返黎(嚟)」睇演唱會，形容見證「老best」被人抬上台，同Chris Martin一同合唱everglow「可能係人生難忘事件之最」。\n\n</p>\n<p>好友更在帖下發布了兩則影片，第一段影片是主唱Chris Martin觀看並分享VICKY三幅自行製造的橫額，一幅上寫着「I travelled 3749 miles to see you. Can you give me this feeling this everglow」（我跨越3749英里來見你。你能給我「永恆璀璨」嗎）；另一幅「Everglow is our pets\\' lullaby」（Everglow是我們寵物的搖籃曲）；並提出要求「Can you sing everglow？」（你可以唱everglow嗎？），Chris Martin答應她的要求與她合唱。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
